Hossein Fateh

We do not break out individual tenant rent, but we can tell you that the
overall return on ACC4 has been better then we expected, we projected on our
IPO being around 12% yield. We now are comfortable in saying that it will be
approximately a 15% yield.

Unidentified Analyst

15%, it sounds great. Also, just a quick question on the FFO. Looking at your
